OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777551071
OL,3,C'Exhausted' Eluned Morgan says 'vote
OL,4,CPlaid Cymru' during election event
OL,6,FAn 'exhausted' Eluned Morgan
OL,7,Faccidentally said "vote Plaid Cymru"
OL,8,Fduring a week-to-go Senedd Election
OL,9,Fevent.
OL,11,FThe First Minister and leader of Welsh
OL,12,FLabour made the slip-up during a
OL,13,Fcampaign event at Barry Island's
OL,14,Fbandstand on Thursday (30 April).
OL,16,FEnding a speech to party members, she
OL,17,Fsaid: "For fairness you can feel, vote
OL,18,FWelsh Labour in the election next
OL,19,Fweek."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
