PN,46103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1777551071
OL,3,C'Exhausted' Eluned Morgan says 'vote
OL,4,CPlaid Cymru' during election event
OL,6,F"Obviously I'm very, very keen for
OL,7,Fpeople to vote Welsh Labour in this
OL,8,Felection. You know where you stand,
OL,9,Fwaiting lists are coming down, nine
OL,10,Fmonths in succession. The plan is
OL,11,Fworking ` don't put it at risk."
OL,13,FPlaid Cymru, Reform UK, Conservatives,
OL,14,FLiberal Democrats and the Green Party
OL,15,Fwere all also out campaigning to mark
OL,16,Fthe one week countdown before voters
OL,17,Fhead to the polls.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
