OL,3,C'Exhausted' Eluned Morgan says 'vote
OL,4,CPlaid Cymru' during election event
OL,6,FIn response to Eluned Morgan's error,
OL,7,Fa Welsh Conservative spokesman said:
OL,8,F"The First Minister has let the cat
OL,9,Fout the bag. Vote Plaid and get
OL,10,FLabour, vote Labour and get Plaid.
OL,11,FThey are two cheeks of the same
OL,12,Fmiserable face."
OL,14,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,15,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,16,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,17,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
